race.description: Magain Fielke Real Estate Gawler Mdn Plate
race.comment: Lots of these look close to getting off the mark. GOLDFIELDS GREY (1) was placed at his first two starts then a solid fourth in tougher company latest. The blinkers are added and draws the inside. Goes close on best. GOOCHEE GAL (6) was a close-up fourth at the mile two back then had to go back from a wide gate last time on the Parks track and was never in it. This is easier and a much better draw. Worth another try. FIABESCA (10) ran in that same race at Morphettville and was good on speed when finishing runner-up. Overdue for a win and will give a sight again. PAGANINI (4) raced this course and distance last time and found the line nicely for second. Drawn wide but will run on hard again. HORSEBACK HEAVEN (7) is fitter for two runs back and is better than the latest effort. Extra trip a plus and fitter again. Can improve.
